Let me analyze the structure and provide a detailed solution.

Main Target Image Analysis:
- The structure appears to be a tower-like construction
- It consists of 7 blocks total
- Has 4 distinct layers from bottom to top
- Uses green, blue, and orange colored blocks
- The top is completed with an orange triangular roof piece

Block Arrangement (bottom to top):
Layer 1: Two blocks (green and orange) side by side
Layer 2: Two blocks (green and orange) side by side
Layer 3: Two blocks (blue blocks) - one full cube and one vertical piece
Layer 4: One orange triangular roof piece

Required blocks from dictionary with their indices:
- Green cubes: #2 (used twice)
- Orange cubes: #3 (used twice)
- Blue cube: #1 (used once)
- Blue vertical piece: #7 (used once)
- Orange triangular roof: #12 (used once)

Assembly sequence:
{
    Step1: Move block with index 2 (bottom left green cube)
    Step2: Move block with index 3 (bottom right orange cube)
    Step3: Move block with index 2 (second layer left green cube)
    Step4: Move block with index 3 (second layer right orange cube)
    Step5: Move block with index 1 (third layer left blue cube)
    Step6: Move block with index 7 (third layer right blue vertical piece)
    Step7: Move block with index 12 (top orange triangular roof)
}
